/* ==========================================
   VINCE TALK TOPICS — WORKING DONE PHASE, LEVEL 1
   phase === "working.done" && friendshipLevel === 1

   CHARACTER: Vince Rossi, Manager at Ruby's Diner
   → Creepy boundary-pusher.
   → Suggests staying around, hints at hanging out post-shift.
   → Player feels mildly uncomfortable but has to remain professional.

   WORKING DONE L1 TONE:
   → Player has finished their 8 hours and is leaving.
   → Vince drops the strict manager routine and becomes "friendly."
   → CRITICAL: Deniable creepiness.

   CONTEXTS:
   dinerRubys_workingDone_morning
   dinerRubys_workingDone_afternoon
   dinerRubys_workingDone_evening
========================================== */

