        shift_review: [
            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/vince/level1/vinceDoneAfternoon-1.webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>Vince looks down at you from a slightly superior angle.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "dinerManager">>I reviewed the dish numbers from today. Above average. Not exceptional, but above average.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Is that a compliment?<</dialog>>
