<<dialog "dinerManager">>It means I noticed you. The other managers just look at employees as drones. I see... potential.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Thanks, Vince.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerManager">>You're very welcome. Run along now.<</dialog>`,
                friendship: 2, trust: 1
            },
            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/vince/level1/vinceDoneAfternoon-3.webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>Vince adjusts his tie closely.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "dinerManager">>You handled the stress of the lunch rush well. Most people break down, get sweaty, get ugly. You remained perfectly composed.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Sweat happens.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerManager">>Not to you. You handled it beautifully. Next shift, I'm expecting the exact same performance.<</dialog>>
