text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/vince/level1/vinceDoneEvening-1.webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>Vince lowers his voice, the lights dimming behind him.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "dinerManager">>It's entirely dark out there now. The city changes its skin at night. Do you like the dark?<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>I like sleeping in it.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerManager">>Such a practical response. Boring, but safe. I prefer people who explore the shadows... but safe is good too.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Night, Vince.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerManager">>Be very careful walking alone. You never know.<</dialog>`,
